{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/1-single-number/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cb9ec761-693d-5def-bc5c-465bb65eb463","excerpt":"Day1 첫번째 문제는 single number 이다.  문제 요약 문제를 요약하면 array 속에 한개만 있었던 숫자를 찾아내라는 것!\n단, 시간복잡도는 O(n)이여야 하고, 공간복잡도는 O(1)이여야 한다. 문제 해결 시간복잡도는 O(n)이여야 하고, 공간복잡도는 O(1)을 지키며 문제를 푸는 방법은 하나다. 4번 XOR 연산자로 찾는 방법!\n나머지 문제의 자세한 솔루션은 여기에 있으니 참고하면 좋다. 1) List operation 시간 복잡도:  O(n^2) 공간 복잡도: O(n)…","html":"<p>Day1 첫번째 문제는 single number 이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"single number\"\n        title=\"single number\"\n        src=\"/static/15f9a064b1b849c39aa864c865eb0a80/e5166/singlenumber.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/15f9a064b1b849c39aa864c865eb0a80/f93b5/singlenumber.jpg 300w,\n/static/15f9a064b1b849c39aa864c865eb0a80/b4294/singlenumber.jpg 600w,\n/static/15f9a064b1b849c39aa864c865eb0a80/e5166/singlenumber.jpg 1200w,\n/static/15f9a064b1b849c39aa864c865eb0a80/f8188/singlenumber.jpg 1494w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>문제를 요약하면 array 속에 한개만 있었던 숫자를 찾아내라는 것!\n단, 시간복잡도는 O(n)이여야 하고, 공간복잡도는 O(1)이여야 한다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>시간복잡도는 O(n)이여야 하고, 공간복잡도는 O(1)을 지키며 문제를 푸는 방법은 하나다. 4번 XOR 연산자로 찾는 방법!\n나머지 문제의 자세한 <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/single-number/solution/\">솔루션</a>은 여기에 있으니 참고하면 좋다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-list-operation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-list-operation\" aria-label=\"1 list operation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) List operation</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>시간 복잡도:  O(n^2)</li>\n<li>공간 복잡도: O(n)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-hash-table\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-hash-table\" aria-label=\"2 hash table permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2) Hash Table</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>시간 복잡도: O(n)</li>\n<li>공간 복잡도: O(n)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-수학적으로-해결-2∗abc−aabbcc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%88%98%ED%95%99%EC%A0%81%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0-2%E2%88%97abc%E2%88%92aabbcc\" aria-label=\"3 수학적으로 해결 2∗abc−aabbcc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3) 수학적으로 해결 (2∗(a+b+c)−(a+a+b+b+c)=c)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>시간 복잡도: O(n)</li>\n<li>공간 복잡도: O(n)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"4-xor로-해결-bit-manipulation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-xor%EB%A1%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0-bit-manipulation\" aria-label=\"4 xor로 해결 bit manipulation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4) XOR로 해결 (Bit Manipulation)</h2>\n<p>XOR 연산자를 사용하면 <code class=\"language-text\">6 ^ 6 ^ 1 ^ 2 ^ 2</code> 의 경우 결과는 <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>이 된다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>시간 복잡도: O(n)</li>\n<li>공간 복잡도: O(1)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {number[]} nums\n * @return {number}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">singleNumber</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nums</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> xor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">item</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> xor <span class=\"token operator\">^=</span> item<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> xor<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"🐤 Single Number","date":"April 02, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/15f9a064b1b849c39aa864c865eb0a80/14b42/singlenumber.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/1-single-number/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/leetcode/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"leetcode","category":"algorithm","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/2-reverse-string/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🏁Reverse String","category":"algorithm","draft":false}}}}}